## âœ… **Pre-check**

âœ”ï¸ Both VMs **must be on same network** (e.g., same Virtual Network in VMware).
âœ”ï¸ Both VMs **should ping each other**:

```bash
ping 192.168.80.131   # from Snort VM
ping 192.168.80.101   # from Kiwi VM
```

âœ”ï¸ Disable Windows Firewall on both VMs:

```bash
# Search: Windows Security > Firewall > Turn off
```

